.TH XIL\-MASTER "1" "2026\-04\-24" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-master
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-master
[-h] (--episode EPISODE | --tag TAG) [--show SHOW] [--daw-dir DAW_DIR] [--output OUTPUT] [--dry-run]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Final Master MP3 Export — mix DAW layers into a single podcast\-ready MP3

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,EPISODE\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S02E03) — derives DAW layer paths

.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Raw tag for non\-episodic content (e.g. V01C03, D01)

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-daw\-dir\fR \fI\,DAW_DIR\/\fR
DAW layer directory (default: daw/<TAG>/)

.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI\,OUTPUT\/\fR
Output MP3 path (default: masters/<TAG>_<slug>_<date>.mp3)

.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be exported without writing files

